{"tid":516000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基督徒中聯辦外祈禱","createTime":"2018-01-01T02:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T06:12:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e33ef2a5f2cd9c76d096d37dc598cb95554df867","tid":516000,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:29:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180101/20261313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180101%2F20261313&d=onFCXyfToMO2LbA4U7NzPkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=1ccfaf92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180101%2F20261313&h=d1da3250\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180101/20261313</a><br />\n<br />\n基督徒中聯辦外祈禱<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n    <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180101/large/01la2p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180101%2Flarge%2F01la2p3.jpg&h=0da58a29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n     <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】有守望內地教會關注組織，昨除夕到中聯辦為中國宗教自由及人權狀況祈禱（圖）。三個基督徒組織包括香港基督徒社關團契、香港基督徒學會及基督徒關懷香港學會，發起人之一的劉志雄牧師稱，2017年中國人權日益惡化，國內基督教會受更大迫害，有內地教會家庭教會禁止聚會，有教堂被強拆，更有大學禁止慶祝聖誕節及向年輕人傳教。劉志雄勉勵教會除在傳福音及慈善事務上努力，更要關注社會公義及民主人權等議題。<br />\n陳善南攝<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t「扭腸B」浚恒母跪求林鄭討公道<br />\n要聞 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t兒童組織評2017施政不合格<br />\n要聞 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t購物城試玩日　商舖全落閘<br />\n要聞 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t新年懷希望　33萬人夾岸賞煙火<br />\n要聞 3小時前"},{"pid":"86fdd249e8d36bb354782fcfaa4d2c6d3fa60ed7","tid":516000,"uid":531,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:32:30.000Z","msg":"佢地有病應該都係企係醫院門口祈禱就得，唔駛入去醫"},{"pid":"6529514bc9025beaaa055fa599883e0ce75daf97","tid":516000,"uid":15872,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:35:56.000Z","msg":"啲耶撚真係on99<